---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import AboutUs from '../assets/Images/AboutUsImage.jpeg';
---

<section
	class="flex flex-wrap lg:flex-nowrap mx-auto bg-lt-gray container-width"
>
	<div class="shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-center w-full lg:w-[35%]">
		<div
			class="relative lg:p-20 lg:max-w- lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:justify-center"
		>
			<h2
				class="w-full mx-auto px-10 pt-10 pb-5 min-h-0 text-[24px] leading-[1.2] text-center lg:text-[45px] lg:p-0 lg:m-0 lg:text-left font-bold"
			>
				Your Trusted Partner in Financial Clarity
			</h2>
			<div
				class="px-7.5 pt-2.5 pb-7.5 text-center max-w-120 mx-auto lg:pt-8 lg:px-0 lg:pb-0 lg:text-left lg:mt-0 font-medium"
			>
				<p class="line-height-1.7">
					At The Big Friendly Bookkeeper, we understand that managing your
					finances can be overwhelming, which is why Matthew Tingley, a seasoned
					CPA and QuickBooks Certified ProAdvisor, is here to simplify the
					process. With over 20 years of experience in bookkeeping and
					consulting, Matt is equipped to handle everything from setting up
					QuickBooks and keeping your books organized, to managing accounts
					payable, payroll, and offering tailored outsourced CFO services.
					Located in Saint John, NB, we pride ourselves on providing friendly,
					personalized service that brings clarity to your financial landscape,
					helping you focus on what really mattersâ€”growing your business.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center max-w-120 mx-auto px-7.5 lg:p-0 lg:m-0">
				<a
					href="/Booking"
					target="_blank"
					class="border-2 border-solid border-primary inline-block shadow-xl w-auto rounded-full cursor-pointer lg:mt-7 lg:mx-0 lg:mb-0 py-3.25 px-10 lg:px-6.25 text-[16px] bg-primary text-white font-semibold hover:opacity-80 mb-10 text-center"
					>Discover How We Simplify Your Finances</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="w-full h-auto lg:w-[65%]">
		<div
			class="m-0 w-full max-w-full h-full max-h-full overflow-hidden lg:content-stretch"
		>
			<Image
				src={AboutUs}
				alt="About Us Image"
				class="object-cover w-full h-full min-h-full lg:relative lg:z-1 lg:block"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
